.auth
    .auth__info
        h2.auth__title АВТОРИЗУЙТЕСЬ
        form.auth__form#auth(name='auth')
            .auth__input
                .auth__input-icon
                    span.fa.fa-user
                input.auth__input-text(type='text' placeholder='Логин')
                span.auth__error
                    span.auth__input-error Введите логин
            .auth__input
                .auth__input-icon
                    span.fa.fa-key
                input.auth__input-text(type='password' placeholder='Пароль')
                span.auth__error
                    span.auth__input-error Введите пароль
            label.auth__check-label
                input.auth__checkbox(type='checkbox')
                | Я человек
            span.auth__robot Вы точно не робот?
            .auth__radio
                label.auth__radio-label
                    input.auth__radio-button(type='radio' name='robot' value='yes')
                    | Да
                label.auth__radio-label
                    input.auth__radio-button(type='radio' name='robot' value='no')
                    | Не уверен
    nav.auth__nav
        a.auth__nav-item.auth__back-button(href='#back') На главную
        button.auth__nav-item(type='submit' name='enter' form='auth') Войти